4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed to transition students into cybersecurity specialists without requiring prior experience. Over a duration of 16 weeks, students participate in three live online classes per week, in groups of up to 18. The curriculum covers Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by numerous institutions. Classes are available in English and Spanish, and the median annual salary for U.S. cybersecurity professionals is approximately $103,560. For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop